latestPosts.caption:
🌲🏔️🌷👭🏻💕see my Uttarakhand trip vlog in my YouTube channel mentioned in my bio!

#uttarakhand #uttarakhanddiaries

Living my childhood again 🎠🦋 
I was here 23 years ago with my mom dad, mama, mousi and cousins. I barely remember anything but it still hits me differently. I used to call it “dinosaur ka zoo” as it has a statue of a dinosaur 🦖 in the center of the zoo. I had so much energy, excitement and living my fullest. I was so happy that day! 
Being there was exceptional✨☺️ lived every steps of it🐾
